about  the  research  that  he  is  doing,  because  after  all,  there  are  so
many  other  areas.  Isn’t  it  better  for  him  to  be  doing  this  research
to  try  to  fight—if  he  can’t  fight  it  for  everything,  isn’t  it  good  for
