someplace  else,  as  you  said,  but  to  say  that  cognitive  research  is
not  short-term,  and  to  say  that  if  we  can  do  it,  it  is  not  a  major
economic impact, I think is wrong.

Mr. ROHRABACHER. Okay. Thank you, Mr. Chairman.
