puter,  and  they  are  in  the  process  now  of  acquiring  and  building
what  they  believe  will  be  the  14th  fastest  computer  in  the  world.
And  the  cost,  I  don’t  want  to  quote  it,  but  it  seemed  to  me  infini-
tesimally  smaller  than  the  supercomputers  that  I  saw  just  eight
years ago at the University of Minnesota.

