taking naturally-expressed direction.

So  when  you  are  dealing  with  Sherman  with  his  concerns  that
you  wish  to  allay,  I  get  a  letter  saying  not  to  worry.  But  when  I
look on your web page it is with the intention of developing a com-
puter that will pass the test put forward by some as to when com-
puters equal human intelligence, and that is to have a natural con-
versation,  and  as  I  say,  able  to  reason,  learn  from  their  experi-
